title: Choose the roles you need
subtitle: This step is divided into section,jobb families and job roles.
subtitle1: You will need to tell supplier how many of each job role you need in each job family section.
subtitle2: Each section contains job families from the government DDaT(Digital,Data and Technology)profession.Each job family contains more information about the roles and what they do
subtitle3: Enter a number for how many staff you need for each family,If you don't need a specific role,youo do not need to enter a number.
subtitle4: Each role has a SFIA level.SFIA defines the skills an dcompetencies required by professionals who design,develop,works and the different level.
